snippet.title: The Leviathan's Fantasy | Game Trailer
snippet.description:
This is a Simulation game. You will manage your cloud city, recruit adventurers all over the world, take them for exploration, obtain resources and blueprints. Construct buildings, make equipment, produce items, so to develop your city into greatness together with your adventurers.
 
#PCGaming #PCGames #GameTrailers
